Method Detail

trackReceived

void trackReceived(GPSTrack track)
Should indicate that some GPS track data have been transmitted and received. A track is a collection of one or more consecutive positions. Note that this method may be called every time a single pair of track coordinates is transmitted.

Parameters:
track - The track data being transmitted.
